{"tid":421234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【血腥鎮壓加獨】西班牙警掟加泰人落樓梯","createTime":"2017-10-02T05:36:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T08:26:35.000Z","uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"832f3fb70d57ce54a9e1426dfa5ef09e6fba5091","tid":421234,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T05:36:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20171002&amp;guid=57279930&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20171002%26guid%3D57279930%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&d=eWIWh0ev6rHAwRz%2FCIq26dibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=69e1ab91\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20171002%26guid%3D57279930%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&h=d4d7349c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20171002&amp;guid=57279930&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n西班牙政府一直打壓周日舉行的加泰羅尼亞獨立公投，周日早上有警察執行封鎖票站的命令時用暴力清場，多名手無寸鐵的民眾慘被警員推落樓梯。<br />\n<br />\n獨立公投在當地引發警民衝突，警方以武力多個封鎖票站，暴力行徑在網上流傳。片中可見其中一個票站有民眾坐在地上抵抗，但被警員一一帶走，有警員朝加泰居民身體上用力踩下去，以及踢向坐在地上的民眾。<br />\n<br />\n警方強行突破樓梯時，有如「撻生魚」般將民眾推下樓，令多人失足跌倒。居民雖然極力阻止警方進入票站，但這個票站仍告失守。有當地人說，他們都是見到警方的暴力手法後，更加激發他們出來投票。"},{"pid":"0151a74a55221a6ce499ede9200cd2c1387ce514","tid":421234,"uid":4324,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T05:38:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0f0c93246f4367a74a615116dde686c02df4a59","tid":421234,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T05:41:27.000Z","msg":"香港都可能會咁樣第時<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a83503714e906a4bf4b4098b4fe269eb2c89b78e","tid":421234,"uid":41477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T05:42:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港都可能會咁樣第時<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港肯定再會暴力好多"},{"pid":"c87b0bdbffdaccc719ffab13ae97ca38707ed73d","tid":421234,"uid":85163,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T05:43:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5f552b5dfe39e78153e35d9ffa9adb8fe9346cba","tid":421234,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T05:44:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/galizarebelde/status/914636241152495616\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgalizarebelde%2Fstatus%2F914636241152495616&d=eWIWh0ev6rHAwRz%2FCIq26dibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=b7a9f09c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgalizarebelde%2Fstatus%2F914636241152495616&h=c0a144b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/galizarebelde/status/914636241152495616</a><br />\n<br />\n仲整斷手指<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af693a3f93c60f69cbf7f332173691959172e295","tid":421234,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T05:44:49.000Z","msg":"唉...左膠人鏈..."},{"pid":"08ab5a5e88b2ab5046c37d71a0527c6e2526620a","tid":421234,"uid":119494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T06:03:50.000Z","msg":"幻覺黎啫 嚇我唔到嘅 <br />\n西方民主國家咁注重人權"},{"pid":"fbc5e26a6fc3427eb9cf427985bb40df68be2c11","tid":421234,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T06:11:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ba1c7b03b4e8c9fa6516dfbb2b90b625fa9a169","tid":421234,"uid":22682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T06:13:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0bonw1xOF-I\" data-